<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>AIR CONDITIONING PROTECTION AND DIAGNOSTIC SYSTEM (APAds&#8482;) DESCRIPTION, OPERATION, TROUBLESHOOTING,
        REMOVE, INSTALL, AND ELECTRICAL CIRCUIT DIAGRAMS MAINTENANCE MANUAL - TROUBLESHOOTING - TESTING APADS
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TESTING APADS</title>
        <specpara>
            <important>
                <para>Once installed, APADS may immediately diagnose existing A/C system faults. For this reason,
                    testing must be completed to ensure the system has been installed correctly and is functioning
                    properly. A troubleshooting guide is included in this manual to assist in diagnosing A/C system
                    faults.
                </para>
                <para>To ensure that the APADS control module is working properly, complete the following tests. If the
                    module displays blink codes or the module is not functioning, consult the troubleshooting blink
                    codes in this section.
                </para>
            </important>
        </specpara>
        <table id="t1602202" frame="all">
            <title>APADS TEST #1</title>
            <tgroup cols="7" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                <colspec colwidth="0.69in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="0.61in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="1.43in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="0.88in"/>
                <colspec colname="col5" colwidth="0.79in"/>
                <colspec colname="col6" colwidth="0.85in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="1.49in"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">TEST POINTS</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES - IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO - OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Turn ignition switch to the ON position and the A/C controls are in the OFF
                                position.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col5">
                            <para>Green light on APAds control module is illuminated.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>After 15 seconds, the A/C compressor clutch should engage.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>After another 15 seconds, the A/C compressor clutch should disengage.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Turn the A/C controls switch ON; listen for the compressor clutch to engage.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Turn the A/C controls switch OFF; listen for the compressor clutch to disengage.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col6">
                            <para>Go to test #2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
        <table id="t1602203" frame="all">
            <title>APADS TEST #2</title>
            <tgroup cols="7" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                <colspec colwidth="0.69in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="0.60in"/>
                <colspec colwidth="1.44in"/>
