                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">TEST POINTS</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES - IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO - OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>OFF</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Turn ignition switch to the OFF position, disconnect the low side pressure switch.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Turn ignition switch to the ON position and the A/C controls are in the OFF
                                position.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col5">
                            <para>Red light on APAds control module will blink four times within 15 seconds.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>OFF</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Turn ignition switch to the OFF position and reconnect the low side pressure switch.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ON/ OFF</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Clear the error code by cycling ignition switch four times (one second ON and one
                                second OFF).
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col5">
                            <para>Green light on APAds control module is illuminated.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col7">
                            <para>Go to blink code troubleshooting chart.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
